{"title":"SR Suntour gets rowdy with bigger enduro forks, more XC shock volume","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/02/sr-suntour-gets-rowdy-with-bigger-enduro-forks-more-xc-shock-volume/","date":1630585003000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-270214\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Besides showing off Olympian Tom Pidcock’s race bike, SR Suntour had a few new and updated suspension forks and rear shocks aimed at everything from all-out Enduro racing to making your XC bike a bit more fun and capable.</p><p>Starting at the rear, the TriAir 2 rear shock gets an additional option with an oblong piggyback reservoir. The transverse placement reduces the height, helping it fit into more frames that a traditional piggyback tube wouldn’t clear.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02075813/sr-suntour-TriAir-piggy-pack-rear-shock-2022-model-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02075813/sr-suntour-TriAir-piggy-pack-rear-shock-2022-model-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:740x555/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"2022 sr suntour tri air rear shock with oblong piggy back reservoir\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02075813/sr-suntour-TriAir-piggy-pack-rear-shock-2022-model-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02075813/sr-suntour-TriAir-piggy-pack-rear-shock-2022-model-1-297x223.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02075813/sr-suntour-TriAir-piggy-pack-rear-shock-2022-model-1-800x600.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/e